To import:

    curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/pmpaulino/terraform-provider-tailscale-membership/main/KEYS \
      | gpg --import

To verify a downloaded release:

    gpg --verify terraform-provider-tailscale-membership_<version>_SHA256SUMS.sig \
                 terraform-provider-tailscale-membership_<version>_SHA256SUMS
    shasum -a 256 -c terraform-provider-tailscale-membership_<version>_SHA256SUMS \
                 --ignore-missing

A successful signature verification establishes that the SHA256SUMS file came
from this project; a successful checksum match establishes that the archive
you downloaded matches what was signed.

